Internal conflict (philosophy)

The second is INFINITELY more compelling.

2. The Remnant as Split Personality = GOLD
Not "Remnant helps him fight."
Remnant is the darkest part of him given form.
Every time he activates it = philosophical debate:

"Let me out. I'll fix this."
