Option C: First Love

Girl/boy he was too afraid to confess to
Social media harassment drove them to it
Protagonist watched it happen online
Rage: "They all watched. They all did nothing."

Option D: Parent

Father/mother crushed by societal pressure
Lost job, lost hope, lost self
Protagonist was too young to understand
Now he understands everything

My Pick: Option C

Ties to social media critique
Most visceral (he watched)
Collective guilt (everyone failed)
Love + loss = maximum pain


