ABILITY 2: "RESONANCE" (Speed/Strength)
Mechanics:

Shiori's emotional state amplifies Haruto's physical abilities
More anger = more speed
More sadness = more strength (weight of grief made literal)
More loneliness = more endurance (isolation = numbness to pain)

Why This Works:

Not generic "power up"
Tied directly to emotions
Different emotional states = different combat advantages

Examples:
Anger Mode:

Blitz speed (like you said—Turbo Granny type)
Erratic, overwhelming
Hard to predict
Cost: Exhausting, can't maintain long

Sadness Mode:

Slow but devastating hits
Each punch feels impossibly heavy
Breaks through defenses
Cost: Haruto feels crushing despair during

Loneliness Mode:

Can't feel pain (emotional numbness extends to physical)
Endures damage that should drop him
Keeps moving like nothing hurts
Cost: Dangerous—might not notice fatal wounds


ABILITY 3: "LAST WORDS" (Psychological Attack)
