Shiori speaks directly to target (through Haruto or manifesting)
Says something only the victim would know
Could be:

Last thing she said
Detail from the assault
Name of someone involved (accomplices)
Truth they've been hiding



Effect:

Psychological break
Confirms: She remembers everything
No escaping truth
Guilt made manifest

