(Perpetrator's face goes pale—he lost that watch, never told anyone)
Perpetrator: "How do you—"
Shiori: "Because I took it. Before I died. To make sure someone would know."

ABILITY 4: "MANIFESTATION" (Full Form)
Mechanics:

Shiori can fully separate from Haruto briefly
Becomes visible to everyone (not just him)
Acts independently
Combat capable

Limitation:

Only lasts 60 seconds max
Extremely draining for both
Haruto vulnerable while she's outside
Used for dramatic reveals or desperate moments

Visual:

She steps out of him (like emerging from water)
Fully solid, visible, real
Can interact with physical world
When time's up: dissolves back into him


THE COST SYSTEM
Using Vestige powers isn't free:
Short-term costs:

Physical exhaustion (Haruto)
Emotional bleed (feels her trauma)
Personality erosion (her emotions linger after deactivation)

Long-term costs:

Haruto losing sense of self (merging identities)
Shiori's memories bleeding into his (he starts "remembering" her death)
Risk: He becomes her, she becomes him—neither exists independently

The Tragedy:

They're saving each other and destroying each other simultaneously
Every battle brings them closer
Every victory erases more of who they were


