The Core Concept:
"RESONANCE"
Simple Definition:
Haruto can make others resonate with Shiori's final moments.
Two Applications:
1. PHYSICAL RESONANCE (Speed + Impact)
What It Does:

Insane speed
When he dashes/moves: impact left behind
Delayed shockwave effect

